## ⚙️ Setup Instructions

### 1️⃣ Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/html-demo.git
cd html-demo
```

### 2️⃣ Build Docker Image

```bash
docker build -t your-dockerhub-username/html-demo .
```

### 3️⃣ Push to Docker Hub

```bash
docker login
docker push your-dockerhub-username/html-demo
```

### 4️⃣ Deploy to Kubernetes

```bash
kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
```

### 5️⃣ Access Application

```bash
kubectl get services
```

Open in browser:

```
http://<NodeIP>:30010
```

